headline: Enphase Energy (NasdaqGM:ENPH) Launches IQ System Controller In France Up 20 kWh
summary: Enphase Energy (NasdaqGM:ENPH) launched the IQ System Controller in France and the Netherlands, a significant development that could correlate with the company's 2% share price increase over the past month. This period also saw the broader market facing a decline of 6%, driven by a steep sell-off amid global trade tensions.
